{"tid":1447891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:20.000Z","uid":91753,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a53ded2a9fc2364ae64f20ea03ca3d01c1f19b","tid":1447891,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"3a4e1b0cccaf7a16500973096d52726409b4a55f","tid":1447891,"uid":143137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"21/7<br />\n11/8<br />\n追究到底"},{"pid":"cf6b2e4d4d7c84ae6f2e2650b792dfb71a16e10e","tid":1447891,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"672501a5c8d7984869ac490d1076176507040f2e","tid":1447891,"uid":68311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"aa97867deb08342ee098d99a82cea5e1a2d8a6b8","tid":1447891,"uid":68311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"8bfc79fbe9e9fc769743c601641279c42bf93366","tid":1447891,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"273b55993297cc60a07df04ad644a7e73bb339b1","tid":1447891,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-u